_sText:
This is a hostage rescue map that takes place at a parking garage.  There are also two buildings near the parking garage that are accessible for sniping.  This is my first map, so let me know what you think or what I should fix.

10/16/08-Fixed minor issues and moved ladders

10/20/08-Finalized the map-changed environment lighting and indoor lighting.  Added some destructible decorative lights.  Added a couple more cars on roof.
